One of the strangest things is that when I was about to sleep, I realised I was only aware of my thoughts. I could not get over the notion that in such a small planet, with such a small ribbon of life, so much goes on.Q. But I really didn't see countries by themselves, I just saw land.Q. On one of the night passes, I dimmed the lights in the flight deck and saw the stars. It isn't one big thing but a number of small things that made us get to where we were at the end.Q. I wanted to go on a canoeing trip and feel the wind in my face. 